            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.Transform(XSharp.__Usual)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Returns a character string from an expression in a format determined by a format code.
      Using TRANSFORM( ) with a large negative number that contains a decimal might result in numeric overflow when that number is passed in as a memory variable. You should use the STR( ) function instead with such numbers.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.Trim(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      删除字符串末尾的空格。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.Trim(System.String,System.Int32,System.String[])</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Remove trailing spaces from a string.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.TString(System.Double)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将指定的秒数转换为时间字符串。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.TString(XSharp.__Usual@)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将指定的秒数转换为时间字符串。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.TToC(System.DateTime,System.Int32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            将 DateTime 表达式转换为指定格式的 Character 值。
        </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.TToD(System.DateTime)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Returns a Date value from a DateTime expression.
        </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.TxtWidth(XSharp.__Usual[])</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para />
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.Unformat(System.String,System.String,System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将转换后的字符串转回其原始值。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.Upper(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将字符串中的小写和混合大小写字符转换为大写。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.Upper(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Returns the specified character expression in uppercase.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.UpperA(System.String@)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将字符串中的小写和混合大小写字符转换为大写，同时更改参数的内容和返回值。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.Val(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将包含数值的字符串转换为数值数据类型。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.Val(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Returns a numeric or currency value from a character expression composed of numbers. You can use VAL( ) to convert the character strings returned by the X# SYS( ) functions to numeric values.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
        </table>
      </content>
